ektionen des msEC Videos in Zeitlupe\n\t\t- Das ursprüngliche Video fürs in den Viewport ziehen kann ich einfach nehmen\n\t\t\t- bisschen schneiden und maskieren\n\t\t- Und dann nehme ich Franks Video und schneide das zu\n\t- [[TODO/MPI Doku]]\n\t\t- MPI genau beschreiben\n\t\t\t- DH Parameter\n\t\t\t- Ursprünge\n\t\t\t- Rigging\n\t\t\t- Collider: Plane, Primitives etc\n\t\t\t- TCP Tool Center Point\n\t\t\t- Fixed Joint: Gripper, wie befestigen?\n\t- [[TODO/Asset Library]]\n\t\t- UR10 für das iPad 9. Gen optimieren [[Carolin Horn]]\n- # Thoughts\n\t- Nicht im Journal die Todo ab-arbeiten, sondern auf den Link klicken und dann dort gucken, was gemacht werden muss",536872126]],["^15",[1060,"^1@",1720152077538,536871756]],["^15",[1060,"^1A","~m1720175627700",536872127]],["^15",[1060,"^Z","journals/2024_07_05.md",536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^K",1720152077534,536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^[",1060,536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^N",20240705,536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^@",true,536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^Y","2024-07-05",536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^11","2024-07-05",536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^B",1720152077534,536871756]],["^15",[1061,"^;","~u6687cd01-6a2d-436a-9383-784b0eb37d62",536872126]],["^15",[1062,"^Q","Fixed Joint: Gripper, wie befestigen?",536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^O","^16",536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^F",1072,536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^X",1061,536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^V",1073,536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^U",4,536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^U",295,536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^U",1061,536871756]],["^15",[1062,"^;","~u6687700d-792f-45e5-bad5-6514dc179f93",536871756]],["^15",[1063,"^Q","### TODOs",536871756]],["^15",[1063,"^O","^16",536871756]],["^15",[1063,"^F",1096,536872123]],["^15",[1063,"^X",1061,536871756]],["^15",[1063,"^V",1061,536871756]],["^15",[1063,"^U",1061,536871756]],["^15",[1063,"^?",["^ ","^1B",3],536872126]],["^15",[1063,"^J",[],536872126]],["^15",[1063,"^;","~u6687700d-9420-46f5-a320-3e9a789150bf",536871756]],["^15",[1064,"^Q","Ursprünge",536871756]],["^15",[1064,"^O","^